statements.sql:
select count(*) as aggregate from `personal` left join (
SELECT
pers_id,
sum(d1) as d1,
sum(d2) as d2,
sum(d3) as d3,
sum(d4) as d4,
sum(d5) as d5,
sum(d6) as d6,
sum(d7) as d7,
sum(d8) as d8
FROM (
SELECT
pers_id,
IF(date = '2018-06-04', sum, null) as d1,
IF(date = '2018-06-05', sum, null) as d2,
IF(date = '2018-06-06', sum, null) as d3,
IF(date = '2018-06-07', sum, null) as d4,
IF(date = '2018-06-08', sum, null) as d5,
IF(date = '2018-06-09', sum, null) as d6,
IF(date = '2018-06-10', sum, null) as d7,
IF(date = '2018-06-11', sum, null) as d8
FROM (
SELECT
sum(worktime) as sum,
pers_id,
date
FROM personal_times
WHERE date BETWEEN '2018-07-04' AND '2018-07-11'
GROUP BY pers_id, date
) as pt
) as st
group by pers_id) as at on `at`.`pers_id` = `personal`.`pers_id` where `is_active` = '1' group by `personal`.`id`

select `personal`.`id`, `personal`.`first_name`, `personal`.`last_name`, `personal`.`pers_id`, `d1` from `personal` left join (
SELECT
pers_id,
sum(d1) as d1,
sum(d2) as d2,
sum(d3) as d3,
sum(d4) as d4,
sum(d5) as d5,
sum(d6) as d6,
sum(d7) as d7,
sum(d8) as d8
FROM (
SELECT
pers_id,
IF(date = '2018-06-04', sum, null) as d1,
IF(date = '2018-06-05', sum, null) as d2,
IF(date = '2018-06-06', sum, null) as d3,
IF(date = '2018-06-07', sum, null) as d4,
IF(date = '2018-06-08', sum, null) as d5,
IF(date = '2018-06-09', sum, null) as d6,
IF(date = '2018-06-10', sum, null) as d7,
IF(date = '2018-06-11', sum, null) as d8
FROM (
SELECT
sum(worktime) as sum,
pers_id,
date
FROM personal_times
WHERE date BETWEEN '2018-07-04' AND '2018-07-11'
GROUP BY pers_id, date
) as pt
) as st
group by pers_id) as at on `at`.`pers_id` = `personal`.`pers_id` where `is_active` = '1' group by `personal`.`id` limit 75 offset 0
